citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at
7:11am-7:22am on 27-NOV-18.
inspector honked, knocked, called out loudly. Upon calling phone number provided, contact was made and due to
an outside job change, hours of availability were changed.
